About the Artist

Linya Yan

Illustrator & visual storyteller bridging the poetic depth of Eastern heritage with contemporary design language.
I believe every culture carries a visual rhythm — a hidden pulse that lives in its landscapes, rituals, and everyday objects. My work seeks to capture that rhythm and translate it into images that feel both ancient and immediate.
Drawing from traditional Chinese aesthetics, folk narratives, and the textures of lived experience, I create illustrations that don't just depict stories — they invite you to step inside them.
